translation.es: Fue demasiado. Tranquila. ¡Está fuera de control!

translation.en: Somebody stop this woman. She's on a rampage!
translation.es: Alguien que pare a esta mujer. ¡Está como loca!

translation.en: Ooh! They're ready!
Mmm. Let's see. Very croissant- y.
Wait, why are you the one judging this competition?
Wow, this one is even croissantier.
Dare I say, croissantiest and best.
translation.es: Me arriesgo a decir que es el más croissantoso y el mejor.

translation.en: This is absurd!
Hmm. Mm. Mm.
translation.es: GASOLINERA DESAYUNO DE MOTEL MÁS O MENOS COMPETENTE

translation.en: Mmm.
- What bakery do you work at? - Oh, I don't work at a bakery.
- A restaurant, then? - No, I work at a magazine.
translation.es: - ¿En un restaurante? - No, trabajo en una revista.

translation.en: Ah, a gourmet food magazine! Which one?
Actually, it's just a magazine publisher.
translation.es: En realidad, es una editorial de revistas.

translation.en: I do mostly data processing.
Yeah, bitch, you got beat by a woman off the street!
translation.es: ¡Sí, tonto! ¡Te ganó una mujer común y corriente!

translation.en: Deal with it!
I see.
Here's my card.
Call me if you ever want to quit your desk job
translation.es: Llámame cuando quieras dejar el trabajo de oficina

translation.en: and come work for me.
Your technique needs to be tamed, but I taste your passion.
translation.es: Debes dominar la técnica, pero se nota tu pasión.

translation.en: - You're a, uh, croissant savant. -
Make sure not to eat that card.
It's made of a very thin, toothsome wafer with sugar ink.
translation.es: Está hecha de una oblea finísima con tinta de azúcar.

translation.en: It took me ten years to learn how to make it.
translation.es: Me llevó diez años aprender a hacerla.

translation.en: - Dude, don't let me eat that card, m'kay? - Thank you?
translation.es: No me dejes comer esa tarjeta, ¿sí? Gracias.

translation.en: And now, you can take back your sugar.
Surprise!
My gamby is a cake now?
Whoops. Unfreeze!
Ooh, pins and needles! Don't touch me. Don't touch me right now.
translation.es: Tengo las piernas dormidas. No me toques.

translation.en: Pins and needles! My gamby is a cake now?
translation.es: ¡Tengo las piernas dormidas! ¿Mi abuela es un pastel?

translation.en: Baked by the Tasty Num Nums award- winning inventor of the crunt.
translation.es: Hecho por el creador de los rosquines y ganador del premio Ñam Ñam.

translation.en: - - We brought croissants, too.
Made out of regular ingredients, not dead people.
translation.es: Hechos con ingredientes comunes, no con muertos.

translation.en: Aw, jeez.
Oh, Speckle, is that you?
Gamby?
Oh, Speckle, my boy! My dearest grand- peep.
Oh, my God, I can't believe it's you!
translation.es: Por Dios, no puedo creer que eres tú.

translation.en: I'm so glad I was baked into a cake
translation.es: Me alegra que me hayan hecho pastel

translation.en: so I could say a proper goodbye and tell you I'm proud of you.
translation.es: para despedirme como corresponde y decirte que estoy orgullosa de ti.

translation.en: Now, Speckle, please eat me.
Gobble me up, sweet child!
I'm trapped between the worlds of the living and the dead,
translation.es: Estoy atrapada entre el mundo de los vivos y el de los muertos.

translation.en: and I need you to eat me so my soul can finally rest!
translation.es: Necesito que me comas para poder descansar en paz.

translation.en: I... I can't!
Be a good boy and eat your gamby!
translation.es: ¡Sé bueno y cómete a tu abuela!

translation.en: Yeah! Eat the ghost cake! Eat the ghost cake!
I guess I could try a little if-- if that's what you want, Gamby.
translation.es: Creo que podría probarlo si eso quieres, abuela.

translation.en: - Mm... - So? How do you like being an architect, baby boy?
It's rewarding work. I'm pretty good at it.
translation.es: Es un trabajo gratificante. Soy bueno.

translation.en: More bureaucracy than I anticipated, though.
translation.es: Pero hay más burocracia de la que creía.

translation.en: You were always a bright one.
Oh, Gamby, you're actually really delicious.
This is the most disgusting and disturbing thing I've ever--
translation.es: Es lo más desagradable y perturbador que vi en mi vida.

translation.en: - Can I have some? - Tuca!
Speckle, sliding down your throat tickles!
translation.es: ¡Speckle! Me da cosquillas pasar por tu garganta.

translation.en: Settle down, Gamby.
Now, would you drink some gin and club soda so I can have a party down here?
translation.es: ¿Podrías beber gin con soda para que tenga una fiesta aquí?

translation.en: Gamby, be quiet!
Wow, so this all worked out pretty great, huh?
Oh, God, Speckle. I'm sorry I gave your sugar away.
translation.es: Cielos, Speckle, lamento haber regalado tu azúcar.

translation.en: If you don't wanna live with me anymore, I understand.
translation.es: Si no quieres seguir viviendo conmigo, lo entenderé.

translation.en: Don't want to live with you? Of course I want to live with you.
translation.es: ¿Si no quiero vivir contigo? ¡Claro que quiero vivir contigo!

translation.en: Really?
Yeah! You know when you're coming home late at night?
translation.es: - ¿En serio? - ¡Sí! ¿Sabes cuando regresas tarde a casa?

translation.en: Yeah?
And everything inside looks so warm and yellow,
translation.es: ¿Cuando todo adentro se ve cálido y amarillo

translation.en: and everything outside is so blue?
translation.es: y afuera todo se ve azul?

translation.en: I love thinking about how, from now on,
translation.es: Me gusta pensar que, desde ahora,

translation.en: this little piece of yellow is for us,
our warm home together.
That's pretty gooey, huh?
Aw, you guys.
Okay, I'll bounce so you can get all mushy.
translation.es: Bien, me iré para que puedan ponerse sentimentales.

translation.en: I guess I'll finally get my box of stuff out of your way.
- Then I'll be all done moving out. - Great idea!
You know, Tuca, if you wanna leave your box here, you can.
translation.es: Tuca, si quieres dejar la caja aquí, puedes hacerlo.

translation.en: - Really? - Or you can just take it.
- Right now. - We've got room.
Then you can just come over whenever you need anything in it.
translation.es: Así podrás venir cuando necesites algo de la caja.

translation.en: - Yeah? - Sure!
Aw. That would be great.
Let's see, it only has my toothbrush, my daily medication--
translation.es: Tiene mi cepillo de dientes, mi medicación diaria...

translation.en: Oh, well, you don't have to leave every--
translation.es: Bueno, no tienes que dejar todo...

translation.en: All my underwear, my sex toys.
Maybe just pick up the box and then, like, take it?
This will be great. My EpiPen, smoke detector batteries,
translation.es: ¡Será genial! Mi epinefrina, baterías para el detector de humo,

translation.en: bike pump, old porn, new porn, frying pan, screwdriver...
translation.es: inflador de bicicleta, pornografía vieja y nueva, una sartén, un destornillador...

translation.en: All right, gang, let's get this wingding bash- a- roo a- ragin'! - Agh! - Ooh!
translation.es: Muy bien, amigos. ¡Comencemos esta fiesta loca!
